{"tid":1899411,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"地區警務工作須重回正軌  3月1日起第2及3梯隊調回各警區","createTime":"2020-02-26T14:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T15:12:38.000Z","uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"76719280d61d978709261421809dc4bb32e37b7b","tid":1899411,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=110603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dnews1%26id%3D110603&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=890d753a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=110603</a><br />\n自6月9日專門應對反修例的「踏浪者行動」(Operation Tiderider)開始，各警區抽調大量前線人員人手到各「總區應變大隊」，集中人手與資源應付，變相是削弱了地區警力。<br />\n<br />\n歷時約7個月的反修例示威，至去年12月起，激烈示威稍稍平息，接着爆發武漢肺炎疫情，抗爭活動聲勢減弱。由於激烈示威活動漸趨減少，各警區可集中人手處理查案工作。據了解，警隊高層經評估後，認為暴亂規模與頻密度減少，決定逐步將地區警務工作重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，下周日(3月1日)起，各總區應變大隊的「第3梯隊」人員率先調回各警區，這批包括資歷較淺或老差骨等，這批人一般未受機動部隊訓練；一周後，即3月8日起，「第2梯隊」的刑偵人員及曾接受機動部隊訓練的人員亦返回警區，重拾調查及反罪惡巡邏工作，例如CID可返回刑事調查隊查案等。同一時間，各警區亦由目前分2更制，每天12小時，變回每天上班8小時的3更制。當「第2及第3梯隊」人員返回警區後，人手亦較充裕，可以補充數十至逾百人不等。<br />\n<br />\n然而，各警區需要自行評估是否全脫下防暴裝，換回藍色制服，但管理層認為大前提須優要顧及同事的安全，但相信在周六、日及一些示威常現的特別日子，如「7.21」、「8.31」等，負責相關職務的人員仍然需要穿上防暴裝。"},{"pid":"2ff9d79800abb3e3ca106151800f4b1bdfb52776","tid":1899411,"uid":126621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"連黑警都覺得社會回復平靜"},{"pid":"14ad11a68fd4843fe12f63f12d6690cea3f1a9bd","tid":1899411,"uid":189157,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"靠你地革命死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2025449804232a904b922620b9ab203c8d68a7","tid":1899411,"uid":29982,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"手足休息完可以再出黎喇"},{"pid":"c2e98a15268b5fc3cd0917493bf9743a5b93ffa2","tid":1899411,"uid":182454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"手足=condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1aa2148736a9b62e988865e60c68619f7fbc990","tid":1899411,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759ceec7dcc29914ddbd38ee8c6d0cf349890721","tid":1899411,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"我懷疑 低層散仔都唔想重回正軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一來, 無得再呃OT<br />\n大家有時會見到夜晚果陣, 一班防暴警 企係到吹水, 但明明周圍無示威<br />\n<br />\n二來, 重回正軌, 即係表示佢地要換番 普通制服去行咇<br />\n輕則被身邊既市民屌, 重則有D勇武係呢個時候行動就................"},{"pid":"fd717a2ae0c46bc5aa797bc80b43fb26672f22ec","tid":1899411,"uid":13724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"換返普通裝備就要小心中武漢肺炎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addf016a84ba64dca0a1232f3a5880fc438f6265","tid":1899411,"uid":205937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd717a2ae0c46bc5aa797bc80b43fb26672f22ec","tid":1899411,"uid":13724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"換返普通裝備就要小心中武漢肺炎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"三萬thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789051a4d4e50ed703a71f9f79a798421f1b8f16","tid":1899411,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14ad11a68fd4843fe12f63f12d6690cea3f1a9bd","tid":1899411,"uid":189157,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"靠你地革命死得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"其實場抗爭未算完<br />\n現在只係將 第2第3梯隊調番所屬位置<br />\n第1梯隊繼續戒備緊<br />\n<br />\n當有一日, 政府總部/警察總部/各區警局 外面既水馬移走<br />\n即係證明政府唔驚再有人衝擊, 可以移走水馬<br />\n咁先算係真正完<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗以政府既膽量<br />\n就算無哂大型示威, 至少都要等多兩三個月, 確保真係無哂示威, 先敢移走"},{"pid":"9c85aa31cd3e15cd36b192440cd2ea1b0aaf1d08","tid":1899411,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"行咇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b27b85dc7c86a6de40b27e756da97bd227cea7","tid":1899411,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"咁幫手睇住隔離營"},{"pid":"92cba9364f7bb6e47071286c4fcf99917aa485bd","tid":1899411,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"企響街都唔做嘢<br />\n哩番入狗屋就更加唔撚做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ca89e8f4c0b21f05ffd3d66470466d63eb0830","tid":1899411,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92cba9364f7bb6e47071286c4fcf99917aa485bd","tid":1899411,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"企響街都唔做嘢<br />\n哩番入狗屋就更加唔撚做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"重回正軌 = 要行咇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9996969d1d357f0dab9b11e020466a8223be84","tid":1899411,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":